# ============================================================================
# WORDPRESS INTEGRATION SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================================================
#
# You mentioned you have WordPress Client ID and Secret!
# Please update the .env file with your actual credentials:
#
# 1. Open .env file
# 2. Find the WordPress OAuth section
# 3. Replace the placeholder values:
#
#    WORDPRESS_CLIENT_ID=<paste-your-actual-client-id-here>
#    WORDPRESS_CLIENT_SECRET=<paste-your-actual-client-secret-here>
#
# 4. If you also have your WordPress site URL and credentials:
#
#    SKYY_ROSE_SITE_URL=https://your-actual-site.com
#    SKYY_ROSE_USERNAME=your-actual-username
#    SKYY_ROSE_PASSWORD=your-actual-password
#    SKYY_ROSE_APP_PASSWORD=your-actual-app-password
#
# 5. Save the .env file
# 6. Run: python scripts/wordpress/quick_status.py
# 7. Verify all credentials show as configured
#
