#   • wordpress_upload_media - Upload images/media
#   • wordpress_get_media - Retrieve media library
#
# Theme & Customization:
#   • wordpress_get_theme_info - Get theme details
#   • wordpress_customize_theme - Customize theme
#   • wordpress_divi_builder - Manage Divi layouts
